  <div class="main content-container" role="main">
    
      <div class="article-teaser">
        The TfL Supplier Awards is our chance to recognise the excellent work our supply chain does for us, and the contribution that a wide range of companies make to running and improving transport in London.
        
      </div>
    
    
      
      
           
      <div class="clearfix">
    <div class="image-box right-float">
    
        
        
        <img src="/cdn/static/cms/images/tfl-suppliers-awards-2017_rdax_400x250.jpg" alt="TfL Supplier Awards 2017 at the London Transport Museum" />
        <span class="caption">TfL Supplier Awards at the London Transport Museum</span>
        
        
    </div>
    <p>The 2018 TfL Supplier Awards ceremony will take place at the London Transport Museum on Wednesday 5 December.</p>
<p>This year, the awards are open to all our suppliers for their efforts in a range of areas, from increasing opportunities for those underrepresented in the workplace to their work to protect the environment. </p>
 </div>
   <div class="pull-quote">
    
        <div class="quote-body">"We are excited to open up our Supplier Awards again for nominations, following their success last year. It's important to recognise all of the hard work that our suppliers put into keeping Londoners and visitors on the move. I urge our suppliers to put themselves forward, so that they can be recognised for their positive impact on the Capital."</div>
        <div class="quote-footer">
            <div class="quotee-name">David Wylie</div>
            <div class="quotee-job-title">Chief Procurement Officer, TfL</div>
        </div>
    </div>
   <p>We're inviting submissions in the following categories:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Health, Safety and Environment</li>
    <li>Efficiencies and Innovation</li>
    <li>Collaboration</li>
    <li>Diversity and Inclusion</li>
    <li>Small and Medium Enterprise
    </li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://www.surveymonkey.co.uk/r/SAwards2018 "><strong>Submit your interest in being considered for TfL's 2018 Supplier Awards</strong></a><strong><a href="https://www.surveymonkey.co.uk/r/SAwards2018 ">.</a></strong></p>
<p>Submissions open from Wednesday 15 August and close on Tuesday 11 September.</p>

 
 
<div>




<p>Read the full list of categories and evaluation criteria:</p>
