 <div>

<p>Last year, there were 80 submissions and Siemens were recognised as TfL's Supplier of the Year. They had proven themselves to be an outstanding supplier, working with us to support women back into employment and developing the potential of those already in the transport industry. They also developed their operational practices when installing traffic signals to increase efficiency and reduce the impact on customers and have been a key part of the success of delivering 36 trains per hour on the Victoria line.</p>
<h3>Some of our 2017 winners </h3>
